WERBEL NAMED 'BUILDER OF THE YEAR' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Roger Werbel, president of Werbel Homes, has been chosen as "Builder of the 
Year" by the Building Industry Assn. of Southern California. 
</P>
<P>
 A member of the association since 1969, Werbel is also a past president and 
life director of the California Building Industry Assn. and a life director of 
the National Assn. of Home Builders. He was recognized by his peers for his 
outstanding contributions to the advancement of the building industry in 
Southern California. 
</P>
<P>
 Werbel Homes has been active in the Southern California home-building market 
since its founding in 1961. The company currently builds in the Antelope 
Valley. 
</P>
