<P>
 * TRAIN STATION: The Vincent Grade/Acton Station, which was completed in five 
days by workers from the Los Angeles County Department of Public Works and Navy 
Seabees, opens Monday.The first train will depart at 5:17 a.m. Take the Angeles 
Forest Highway exit off the Antelope Valley (14) Freeway. The station is on 
Sierra Highway just south of the intersection of Sierra Highway and Angeles 
Forest Highway. 
