<HEADLINE>
<P>
SUPER BOWL XXVIII / BUFFALO BILLS VS. DALLAS COWBOYS; SUPER BOWL TROPHY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Winning team receives possession of the Vince Lombardi Trophy, a sterling 
silver trophy created by Tiffany & Co. It was named for the late Vince Lombardi 
before Super Bowl V. Trophy consists of regulation-size silver football mounted 
in a kicking position on a pyramid-like stand of the concave sides.The trophy 
stands 20.75 inches, weighs 107.3 ounces, and is valued in excess of $10,000. 
The words "Vince Lombardi Trophy" and "Super Bowl XXVIII" are engraved in the 
base along with the NFL emblem. 
</P>
