<TEXT>
<P>
 Times reporters listened to the voices of the people in the days following the 
quake, recording memories in homes, workplaces, in the encampments of the 
earthquake homeless. 
</P>
<P>
 The stories are not alike. But they share a devotion to family and duty. 
</P>
<P>
 Section T, a special report. 
</P>
</TEXT>
