<DOCNO> LA013094-0285 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 008632 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 30, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 5; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
