</P>
<P>
 Sylmar Tahitian Mobile park in Sylmar. 64 mobile homes destroyed. SANTA 
CLARITA 
</P>
<P>
 Heritage Junction Mitchell Adobe Schoolhouse Pardee house 
</P>
<P>
 Mentryville home (1893) Piru mansion West Greenbrier mobile home park William 
S. Hart mansion VENTURA COUNTY 
</P>
<P>
