</P>
<P>
 Church of Nazarene Grandma Prisbrey's Bottle Village The Church of Jesus 
Christ of Latter-Day Saints (Erringer Road) Maier House (1911) Santa Susana 
Railroad Depot (1903) Simi Valley Community Church Simi Valley High School 
