 SANTA YNEZ -- The 12th annual Santa Barbara County Vintners' Festival isn't 
until April 23-24, but many tickets have been sold through a random drawing. 
Remaining tickets become available Tuesday on a first-come, first-served 
basis.Tastings, music and viticultural exhibits, 1-4 p.m. both days at Flag Is 
Up Farm, Solvang. $50 per day. (805) 688-0881. LA JOLLA -- "Artists on the 
Cutting Edge II," a series of literary/musical presentations, continues in 
Sherwood Auditorium at the Museum of Contemporary Art, La Jolla. 7:30 p.m. this 
Thursday and Feb. 10, 17, 20, 24 and March 3 at 700 Prospect St. $12 per event; 
$10, students, seniors or museum members. (619) 454-3541. CALISTOGA -- Have a 
